{"tid":1989361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"急關邊境！緬甸爆發武裝衝突 3發砲彈打到中國","createTime":"2020-04-26T01:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T02:36:25.000Z","uid":30561,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"31070122219795e6094ee9f58a073e2a1d710630","tid":1989361,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:52:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3145073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3145073&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=fc18e6fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3145073&h=88c31852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3145073</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/04/24/phpEiraSR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F04%2F24%2FphpEiraSR.jpg&h=3f7fc015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸在2018年，與中國相鄰的邊境城鎮也曾爆發武裝衝突，當時有3枚火箭彈落入中國。圖為緬甸火箭彈。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國西南邊境為軍事衝突熱點，緬甸23日晚間，與中國邊境的城鎮發生武裝衝突，過程中有3枚砲彈落入中國境內，集中當地建築物，中方緊急關閉邊境口岸。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《央視軍事》報導，緬甸當地23日晚間，與中國相鄰的「木姐」邊境城鎮爆發武裝衝突，當地流出的影片能見武裝份子手持武器，當地1間加油站受到襲擊，中方獲悉至少有3枚砲彈落入中國雲南省境內，中國民眾指出，姐告邊境貿易區內的1所小學「被炸了」。<br />\n<br />\n《央視軍事》指出，姐告邊境貿易區還有其他建築物以及車輛受到波及，但目前暫時沒有人員傷亡數據，中方對此已經緊急關閉姐告邊境口岸，短時間內不與緬甸端有所往來。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，緬甸木姐在2018年5月就曾爆發流血軍事武裝衝突，當時緬甸政府軍隊、警察部隊，和緬甸少數民族在當地開戰，造成2名中國公民死亡，還有3枚火箭彈與多發流彈落到中國境內，中方當時透過外交部對緬甸進行嚴正交涉，要求立刻停火。"},{"pid":"38d646be26bb24a3df2ff8acf65cba39245dbd2c","tid":1989361,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:53:07.000Z","msg":"真係打就會縮返入去，唔擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd69bba28b54b1980b9d34c7f119c19863517ac","tid":1989361,"uid":30561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"請問是否如法官對犯人所講的高尚情操 一樣咁高尚？"},{"pid":"92edcaecb54f9b79c1c45485f2b3952eed3fb8ed","tid":1989361,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"從lee件事會睇到 支那狗如果真係會打仗<br />\n又洗撚鬼鬼鼠鼠放毒咩"},{"pid":"ebf2ca1ee22c514dc1b5591333c6ff7552cbff9f","tid":1989361,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"嚴正交涉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703c81d5ec4eeb5bfbbecdda7b4c9e5d8767e4cb","tid":1989361,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92edcaecb54f9b79c1c45485f2b3952eed3fb8ed","tid":1989361,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"從lee件事會睇到 支那狗如果真係會打仗<br />\n又洗撚鬼鬼鼠鼠放毒咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"常規戰肯定連越南都打唔嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbbd0dff150dc350cc4b8e921c99cc0500c848b","tid":1989361,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f74b7d4a35b4c23a39d72769bbb0bc6c94bb0f","tid":1989361,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"昂山素姫算唔算係極端緬甸本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567e04e58e9ff89ef4566d173aff52104be14600","tid":1989361,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f74b7d4a35b4c23a39d72769bbb0bc6c94bb0f","tid":1989361,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"昂山素姫算唔算係極端緬甸本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":